        - `ListMappingsBySymbol` now resolves taxonomy categories by full `(source, taxonomy, market, code)` composite key instead of `code` alone, avoiding cross-taxonomy collisions
        - Parent-category chain is now loaded when enriching `by_security` responses so PhoenixA can classify `derived_flags.financial_sector` at subtree level without pushing those semantics back into the raw ODS taxonomy table
        - Added `taxonomy_category_derived_flags` as a dedicated PhoenixA-derived persistence layer for taxonomy semantic flags; `taxonomy_category.attrs_json` is now only treated as a backward-compatible read fallback
        - Updated docs and API validation scripts to reflect the canonical field contract
